{"tid":1525739,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【We Connect】來自中東，加勒比海嘅新同學都關心香港","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:47:42.000Z","uid":296674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"757b32a43eb20c9161e982884021e4f52b2b96e6","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"又係我銀叉巴<br />\n知道831之後大家沮喪嘅沮喪、憤怒嘅憤怒、無力嘅無力<br />\n我睇直播，都覺得有心無力<br />\n身在幾千公里以外，我又可以做啲乜呢？<br />\n我就忽然間醒起，過去嗰兩個禮拜遇見嘅新同學<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>西方大學國際化，去得嘅都係本國嘅精英、權貴仔女，呢個就係海外文宣嘅兵家必爭之地</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n話說我上堂隔離果個人來自<span style=\"color: orange;\">中東黎巴嫩</span>（Lebanon），係近亞地區少數擁有民主自由法治嘅國家；經歷過內戰，仍然能夠堅持開放包容嘅社會實在少之又少<br />\n第一日自我介紹，我一話自己來自香港，佢即刻話「<span style=\"color: violet;\">香港而家點呀？好似大檸樂喎</span>」<br />\n我要上堂，冇時間一一解釋，但係我有成個sem慢慢教育呢位新朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有有一日係學校大樓外面遇到個陌生人，都係學生，但係我從來未見過<br />\n佢來自<span style=\"color: orange;\">法國位於加勒比海嘅海外大區馬丁尼克（Martinique）</span><br />\n講真我成世人都未聽過呢個地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住佢同我講，佢有<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽開Podcast，從而認識香港局勢</span><br />\n我發現香港同埋馬丁尼克地位相近：兩個都係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>憲法上屬於某大國嘅一部分，幾十年來都有爭取更大自主權嘅運動</strong></span></span>；當然始終因為法國係民主自由國家，馬丁尼克嘅運動有初步成功<br />\n佢又有同我講，佢覺得雖然<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>馬丁尼克係法國嘅一部分，但係因為文化差異，馬丁尼克人唔係法國人</strong></span></span> <br />\n呢個講法係咪有啲似曾相識呢<br />\n<br />\n嗰刻我有少少感動 估唔到香港呢個彈丸之地 真係能夠衝出國際<br />\n我哋要繼續發揮小宇宙 做得好好睇睇 <br />\n我哋要成為全球七十億人嘅榜樣同埋爭取民主自由法治嘅人嘅希望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n無論去到天涯海角 大家都一定會有同路人<br />\nBe humble Be water <br />\n香港人加油<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe time is always right to do what is right －－Martin Luther King Jr. （馬丁路德金）"},{"pid":"817dfce6cd46742a8d6bf815ab96c343e7b99920","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09630a86e2f835f8068b5a224f3bbc89b0f8ed6b","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"206552694944c88344e8b4be03940213ce7b7bf8","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2b8ce367a4d23b6f0202b95c3ae6fd7b9646d7fd","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6264b1d8051798d6e8c62c85f245d1c14cef3320","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"e6f161c85479b5fdbf2db9fe5372846395a2d077","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"1a4e87f1ee09579f1d2b501ba41628e307ac8336","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"5373d248c5468dae5291d40c6da9f975386e267d","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推"},{"pid":"e29dd5763632a8ec33c76217e45aa944e7f18455","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推"},{"pid":"5e3a73bbd4a845acc0321f4a7477b7659e343f3f","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推"},{"pid":"5dd3396e1789611cbf0c34c6efbe9a085b21cc96","tid":1525739,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"小弟會馬不停蹄咁做實體文宣，大家放心<br />\n大家只要做好本份、擇善固執，我就有無限彈藥<img src=\"